[recipe] | #cuisineparadiseMealPlanner
Dinner tonight serve with Air-fried Herbal Chicken Wing, Stir-fry Broccoli with mushroom and carrot plus White Fungus & Lady Bell Pork Rib Soup
.
今晚的菜单：玉竹沙参雪耳汤搭配气炸药材鸡翅和炒椰菜花。玉竹沙参雪耳汤可以帮助理气顺气和滋阴润肺或缓和心烦气燥和虚劳烦热。是秋日养生药膳并且适合男女老少都适合饮用
.
.
🥣SOUP OF DAY
This soup helps to boost up immunity, clear phlegm and remove heatiness trap in the body
.
Ingredients
1 Snow Fungus with Lady Bell Soup Pack
500g soft pork bone/pork fillet 
1.2L water 
1 tbsp wolfberries, optional
.
Method
1. Rinse all the herbs and soaked white fungus for 12-20 minutes. Remove and tear into pieces
2. Blanch pork ribs and in a soup pot bring 1.2L of water to boil
3. Add in all ingredients (except wolfberries) and simmer on low heat on stove for at least 1.5 hours 
ALTERNATIVELY
- you can add everything in slow cooker and cook on auto mode for 2-3 hours
4. Lastly season to taste, add in wolfberries and serve
.
.
📝 Verdict
- the herbs pack from MuMuMummy is very clean and fresh plus it is procured and vacuum packed to maintain its quality
.
.
💰SAVINGS
@mumumummy.sg is now having 25% storewide discount on their herbal soups and tea packs so do checkout their website https://www.mumumummy.com
.
OR - you can also use our promo code “ELLENA”; to enjoy Buy 2 get 1 FREE on their daily soup category
.
.
📕Circuit Breaker Day 53
.
.
.
